        "a_cn": "是。绽火是令被选择的角色自行弃置装备区的所有牌。",
        "q_en": "When God Lu Xun uses [Blaze of Fire] and selects Jie Huang Yueying, does she also discard armor and treasure cards?",
        "a_en": "Yes. [Blaze of Fire] instructs the selected character to discard all cards from their Equipment Zone."
      }
